About

Vitsco, with all the planning ideas developed, is a bridge between blockchain technology as a solution to human needs in the future and various types of human needs which are always developing and progressing very rapidly.

Vitsco is here to fulfill everyone's expectations. Be at the forefront of witnessing history with Vitsco to make everyone's dreams come true.

Why Vitsco?

VITSCO Locked Rewards

Locking at least 1 $VITSCO token through a Lock Smart Contract Service provider (Like PINKSALE, COOKIESALE, etc.) opens up an amazing opportunity for you to become a VIP HODLER entitled to Earn Profit Sharing Royalties from DEFI projects where you can choose the available options.

We value your investment and strive to provide attractive incentives that maximize your earning potential. By holding Vitsco tokens and locking them via Smart Contracts, you become an integral part of a thriving ecosystem that rewards loyalty and dedication.

Cutting-Edge Binance SmartChain Integration

Vitsco operates on the Binance SmartChain network, ensuring lightningfast and secure transactions for our users. With our seamless integration, you can experience the full potential of Binance SmartChain’s capabilities while enjoying the perks of being a part of the Vitsco community.

Community-Driven Army

Vitsco is more than just a cryptocurrency platiorm; it’s an army of individuals who believe in the transformative power of decentralized finance. When you join the Vitsco community, you become part of a strong, united force working towards a common goal: financial freedom. Together, we learn, grow, and support one another on this exhilarating journey.

Empowering User Experience

We understand that navigating the world of cryptocurrencies can be intimidating for newcomers. That’s why we have designed the Vitsco platiorm with a user-friendly interface that simplifies the process for everyone. Whether you’re a seasoned investor or new to the world of digital assets, Vitsco provides an intuitive and engaging experience to ensure your journey is seamless and enjoyable.

Roadmap

THE FIRST STAGE

• Contract Development:
Engage experienced developers to create a secure and efficient smart contract for Vitsco.
• Website Development:
Build a user-friendly and informative website to serve as the main platform for the project.
• Vitsco Stake Pool Development in Cryptopreneur Finance:
Through our Alliance, Cryptopreneur Finance Dexes we are preparing several stake Pools with attractive rewards to raise awareness and excitement among Hodlers before the Vitsco Locked Reward Program is launched.

SECOND STAGE

• Build in LEND/BORROW Defi Project:
VITSCO does not go through pre-sales, Through Cryptopreneur Finance, VITSCO can be BOUGHT & SOLD directly. As compensation for VITSCO holders before the Vitsco Lock Reward program is launched, they can place their VITSCO Tokens in the Stake Pool.
• CFO Project Launch Part 01-02:
Immediately after the Defi Lending/Lending Platform is launched & has been operational for 1-3 months, the CFO Project part 01-02 will be opened to give VITSCO Hodlers the opportunity to participate in the VITSCO Locked Rewards program.
• Build in CRF & PAY WALLET Defi Project:
The Defi CRF & PAY WALLET platform developed is very unique and different from most, because it combines Chat Features, Token Lock Rewards & fee options that will be used in transactions. Of course, when the CFO program opens, it will be interesting to get revenue sharing as a VIP Hodler
• CFO Project Launch Part 03-04
Immediately after the CRF & CCF Wallet Platform is launched & has been operational for 1-3 months, the CFO Project part 03-04 will be opened to give VITSCO Hodlers the opportunity to participate in the VITSCO Locked Rewards program.

THIRD STAGE

• Community Engagement:
Foster an active and loyal community through regular updates and social media interactions.
•Influencer Partnerships:
Complete strategic partnerships with industry influencers, projects, or organizations that align with the project vision.
• Additional Utility Token Development:
Explore and develop additional utility or token use cases to enhance their value proposition through several VITSCO Alliance projects.
• Wallet Integration:
Facilitates the integration of tokens into cryptocurrency wallets to increase accessibility for users.
• Improved Community Governance:
Building a decentralized governance model, allowing token holders to actively participate in the decision-making process.
• Partnerships and Integrations:
Seek collaboration or integration with other projects or platforms to expand the reach and adoption of the token.

FOUR STAGE

• Build in NFT Revshare Defi Project:
Together with the Alliance to Build and develop the Revshare NFT Project to Diversify Financial Development Categories in Blockchain Technology
• CFO Project Launch Part 05:
Immediately after the Defi NFT Revshare Platform is launched & has been operational for 1-3 months, the CFO Project part 05 will be opened to give VITSCO Hodlers the opportunity to participate in the VITSCO Locked Rewards program.
• Build in Liquid Staking Defi Project:
Together with the Alliance to Build and develop the Liquid Staking Project to Diversify Financial Development Categories in Blockchain Technology.
• CFO Project Launch Part 06:
Immediately after the Defi Liquid Staking Platform is launched & has been operational for 1-3 months, the CFO Project part 06 will be opened to give VITSCO Hodlers the opportunity to participate in the VITSCO Locked Rewards program.

FIFTH STAGE

Together with the Alliance to Build and develop the Dex Aggregator Defi Project to Diversify Financial Development Categories in Blockchain Technology
• CFO Project Launch Part 07:
Immediately after the Defi NFT Revshare Platform is launched & has been operational for 1-3 months, the CFO Project part 07 will be opened to give VITSCO Hodlers the opportunity to participate in the VITSCO Locked Rewards program.

Our Road to Success

Inception and Vision

Vitsco was founded with a vision to democratize finance and create financial opportunities for individuals around the world to use Blockchain. Our founders realized the potential of the Binance SmartChain network and the other alliance protocols that have been established will certainly have a huge opportunity to further develop the potential of Blockchain Technology for the future of digital currencies.

Building the Vitsco Army

Our success is driven by the incredible community that has rallied around Vitsco. We have witnessed exponential growth in our army of like-minded individuals who share a common goal of financial empowerment. Through engaging events, educational resources, and a supportive network, we have fostered an environment that encourages collaboration and knowledge sharing.

Strategic Partnerships

Vitsco has forged strategic partnerships with industry leaders, blockchain enthusiasts, and financial experts. These collaborations have allowed us to expand our reach, access cuting-edge technology, and offer innovative solutions to our users. Together, we strive to push the boundaries of what is possible in the world of cryptocurrencies.

Continual Innovation

Our commitment to innovation is unwavering. We are constantly exploring new technologies, refining our platiorm, and expanding our offerings to ensure that Vitsco remains at the forefront of the ever-evolving crypto landscape. Our passion for pushing boundaries and embracing new possibilities drives us to create an exceptional user experience for our army members.
